  "body": "Seems switching from `Component` to `PureComponent` breaks hot reloading, error messages below, it can be reliably reproduced in any project (simply switching back to `Component` will fix the problem).\n\n```\nprocess-update.js:81 [HMR] The following modules couldn't be hot updated: (Full reload needed)\nThis is usually because the modules which have changed (and their parents) do not know how to hot reload themselves. See http://webpack.github.io/docs/hot-module-replacement-with-webpack.html for more details.logUpdates @ process-update.js:81applyCallback @ process-update.js:49hotApply @ bootstrap fccae4c…:531cb @ process-update.js:52hotUpdateDownloaded @ bootstrap fccae4c…:311hotAddUpdateChunk @ bootstrap fccae4c…:283webpackHotUpdateCallback @ bootstrap fccae4c…:4(anonymous function) @ 0.c30c5b2….hot-update.js:1\nprocess-update.js:89 [HMR]  - ./shared/components/Cart.jsx\n```\n",
